item.title: Toolback
item.description: Toolback - Low Code App Builder. An online programming environment, with low code features. Drag and drop a UI and add scripts directly to components. Generate websites and desktop apps (electron based) with a click of a button. Toolback Toolback is the drag and drop UI builder and online, Low Code, app building IDE. Preview your app with a key press. Export to a website or electron app - one click!
